data.output: I was wearing my favourite pumps. I managed to walk through diesel  and get it on the sole of one pump and leave footprints all over my friend's carpet. It's impossible to get out. Even worse than petrol.
My friend asked me to post a letter. I said no. I didn't expect it to send her into a rage and make her stamp her feet.
I went to the Empire comedy club. They still have the old performing organ from when it was a dance hall. i wanted to play the organ, but they said no and I wanted to comply with their rules.
I am waiting for a payment for a quilt I made, based on existential pinciples - I used colours to reflect what it means to exist. But I worry that it's too dark and suggests gloom rather than joy.
